{% comment %}
  Ace Party & Tent Rental - Custom Font Loading

  Brand fonts: Geoform (headings/UI) and Zodiak (body)

  FONT FILE STATUS:
  - Zodiak: Available free from Fontshare CDN
  - Geoform: Commercial font from Production Type. Need .woff2 files from
    client/designer. Using Montserrat fallback until files are available.

  When Geoform files are available:
  1. Add geoform-medium.woff2 to theme/assets/
  2. Uncomment the @font-face block below
  3. Remove Montserrat from --ace-font-heading in ace-brand.css
{% endcomment %}

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://api.fontshare.com" crossorigin>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=zodiak@400&display=swap">

{%- comment -%}
  Geoform - Uncomment when .woff2 files are added to theme/assets/

  <link rel="preload" as="font" href="{{ 'geoform-medium.woff2' | asset_url }}" type="font/woff2" crossorigin>
  <style>
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Geoform';
      src: url('{{ 'geoform-medium.woff2' | asset_url }}') format('woff2');
      font-weight: 500;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }
  </style>
{%- endcomment -%}
